{"tid":601952,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"連登波台新搞作［第一屆］波台球膽皇","createTime":"2018-03-22T15:36:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T18:04:14.000Z","uid":31050,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a4d14c9ecfbd07507fae7ea935b6f8638ae5f555","tid":601952,"uid":31050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T15:36:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知大家有無睇過蘋果日報有10條粉腸各有花名<br />\n日日都係到尻up投注而家連登都有份啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/wongwongballking\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwongwongballking&d=9r6hOT1uquhmcijAzKx0jzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=64ef743c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/wongwongballking</a><br />\n4月1號就正式開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一次為期兩星期<br />\n到最後有最多投注額既巴打有<br />\n高達500蚊獎金<br />\n味到最後都唔知鹿死誰手<br />\n第一期名單 1.山狗 (屙爛屎山奇士)<br />\n2.wai (IT狗)<br />\n3.wa (wa)<br />\n4.盤仔 (盤守操) <br />\n5.ryan (儉仔)<br />\n6.月巴 (月巴零零發)<br />\n7. Wing (Wing)<br />\n8. 時巴 (時巴)<br />\n9.mystery (mystery)<br />\n10. Migos (migos)<br />\n公証人:Gab<br />\n<br />\n絕對唔係圍內玩，每2星期為一轉，最尾果3名會退出位置俾想玩既巴打加入(先留名先得)。<br />\n夠刺激 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今晚買聽日場次 無得改無得睇尾盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同報紙玩法一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家當多份免費報紙睇波 <br />\n決戰紫禁之癲"},{"pid":"dd230c7db8d91b30161c03ea194a7a3a0c74b194","tid":601952,"uid":31050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T15:37:46.000Z","msg":"今晚有採排表演賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係波台宣傳下"},{"pid":"7619347fc38c1139814c8e6f5643afb892723c1e","tid":601952,"uid":31050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T15:39:49.000Z","msg":"推 <br />\n打擊賣料狗<br />\n大眾免費觀看"},{"pid":"8efce2e7c8206ebe5658fec78d52a991b0828833","tid":601952,"uid":31050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T15:45:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"24c7c208759c664803d52c704c2e0792cd799bb0","tid":601952,"uid":1373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T15:51:36.000Z","msg":"想參加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0a8239b73dce4a94c00d20903d1693529395b91","tid":601952,"uid":31050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24c7c208759c664803d52c704c2e0792cd799bb0","tid":601952,"uid":1373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T15:51:36.000Z","msg":"想參加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T15:53:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果發展得好唔知會唔會開多個降班區玩<br />\n英甲/英冠"},{"pid":"debcf5cc468d289df364a6d581b3b3c3cc9721bc","tid":601952,"uid":31050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T15:59:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5784e7722c0b43e98e34894ee18a1e73cc4bebd3","tid":601952,"uid":31050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T16:01:44.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a058f6f1abc3b1ab5d3f0ea2fc002058c1d704d","tid":601952,"uid":1373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0a8239b73dce4a94c00d20903d1693529395b91","tid":601952,"uid":31050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"